|2 |  └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN           |          |1       |17          |
|3 |    ├─SUBPLAN SCAN             |VIEW2     |2       |15          |
|4 |    │ └─UNION ALL              |          |2       |15          |
|5 |    │   ├─TABLE FULL SCAN      |OUTR      |1       |3           |
|6 |    │   └─HASH JOIN            |          |1       |12          |
|7 |    │     ├─NESTED-LOOP JOIN   |          |1       |5           |
|8 |    │     │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN  |INNR      |1       |3           |
|9 |    │     │ └─MATERIAL         |          |1       |3           |
|10|    │     │   └─TABLE FULL SCAN|INNR2     |1       |3           |
|11|    │     └─TABLE RANGE SCAN   |OUTR(idx5)|1       |8           |
|12|    └─MATERIAL                 |          |1       |3           |
|13|      └─TABLE FULL SCAN        |OUTR2     |1       |3           |
=====================================================================
